title: HGB Road Trip 2015 - Nashville
itunes:title: HGB Road Trip 2015 - Nashville
description: History Goes Bump is roadtripping and this is the final episode from the road! Diane and Denise visited Music City, better known as Nashville and took in some of the historic buildings and a ghost tour with Nashville Ghost Tours. On this show, they share a brief history and then the hauntings that take place at some of the historic buildings including the state capitol!
